VAIFORM — ASSETS / PEXELS RULES

Applies to:
- src/services/pexels*.js
- src/routes/assets*.js

Rules:
- Preserve response field names consumed by callers.
- Honor paging and return nextPage when available.
- De-dupe results by provider ID.
- Preserve retry/backoff behavior for provider limits.
- Do not widen this surface into generic asset-contract rewrites without caller/doc verification.
- Verify current callers before renaming or reshaping asset payloads.
